                    <td class="bold">Frontend Core</td>
                    <td>React.js (v18+) with TypeScript for rigorous type-safety and state predictability.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="bold">Canvas Rendering</td>
                    <td>HTML5 Canvas API integrated with Fabric.js / Konva.js for performant vector and image manipulation.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="bold">Styling & UI Components</td>
                    <td>Tailwind CSS coupled with Framer Motion for premium micro-interactions and transitions.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
