                    <td>Node.js (Express) ecosystem optimized for fast file processing and asset orchestration.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="bold">Storage Solutions</td>
                    <td>Cloudinary/AWS S3 for optimized CDN delivery and secure, compressed image storage layers.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>4. Scope of Work & Deliverables</h2>
        <p>The implementation life cycle will progress linearly across distinct implementation milestones to ensure adequate testing and system optimization at each phase:</p>
        
        <h3>Milestone 1: Wireframing & Structural Design</h3>
        <p>Interactive Figma prototyping focused on spatial design, fluid navigation paths, media library organization, and viewport modularity.</p>

        <h3>Milestone 2: Canvas Integration & Canvas Engine Dev</h3>
        <p>Structuring the layout algorithm. Enabling cross-axis image translation, automated border resolution, padding metrics control, and layer sorting options.</p>

        <h3>Milestone 3: Core Features & Asset Pipelines</h3>
        <p>Integrating localized cropping engines, multi-tone color filter arrays, metadata injection, and asynchronous multi-file uploads.</p>

